commit.title: [genarg] Remove some deprecated genargs.
commit.message:
[genarg] Remove some deprecated genargs.

No point on having these aliases; I've tried to choose the more
"informative" names, and keep the invariant wrt to naming that the
OCaml-level id corresponds to the entry-level id.
